  "text": "the corresponding box sizes cover a range of the order L = 0.01 fm . . . 1 fm (or µ in 100 GeV . . . 1 GeV). At each u, three lattice resolutions -L/a = 6, 8, 12 -were simulated, and the numerical results for Z stat A and Σ stat A stemming from the three static discretization s, HYP1 and HYP2 are collected in tables 5 and 6 in appendix B. Statistical errors were estimated by a jackknife analysis and cross-checked with the method of ref. [CITATION_1] .",
